  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MouseWars is a real time multiplayer cursor war game. The cursors have to fight until only one remains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Play online</strong> with your friends or practice with <strong>bots</strong> </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play an exclusive offline, <strong>local multiplayer mode</strong> by plugging multiple USB mice, or gamepads</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Two game modes: <strong>All vs all</strong> and <strong>Team vs team</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Two score types: <strong>Deathmatch </strong>and <strong>Survival</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>9</strong> types of attacks</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Up to <strong>8</strong> players per room </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In-game <strong>chat</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
